<br>
your hunting party is doomed if your wizard has taken the name Ooops Mybad.<br>
<br>
if the barbarian warrior says, &quot; I have a plan&quot;, your hunting party is doomed.<br>
<br>
when asked what bow he uses the ranger puffs up and says, &quot; I don't throw twigs, I use this...&quot; and brandishes a two handed sword, the party is doomed.<br>
<br>
if You hear Your cleric say she will back up heal only, because she is a tank.<br>
<br>
when Your enchanter, who has reached the highest circle of spells there is, doesn't know what Kodiacs Endless Intellect is, Your party is surely doomed to failure<br>
<br>
if Your monk has never in His career practiced mend, didn't know He could play dead, and is currently carrying so much that His attacks are less effective and He gets hit more often. ( ooc is over the 15 lb weight limit )<br>
<br>
Your party is doomed when the shaman looks at You blankly when told to make creatures lethargic ( slow ) and He says He has no spells to do that.<br>
<br>
if Your front line fighter looks at You and says &quot; what, there is something better then bronze?&quot;<br>
<br>
when the beastlord who has the ability to speak with 59 beasts is still fighting with the bear that came to Him when He could only speak to 39 beasts.<br>
<br>
Your druid has no clue what You are asking about if You ask for some sort of damage shield.<br>
<br>
Your shadow knight says she doesn't know what harm touch does.<br>
<br>
if You notice Your paladin is always managing to lay hands on the enemy instead of members of the hunting party, the party is doomed.<br>
<br>
You have just overheard Your shadow knight complain that His gear doesn't have enough wisdom enhancing magic on it.<br>
<br>
Your mage doesn't know the difference between the earth pet and the air pet, and the parties rogue, has to explain it to them.<br>
<br>
Your necromancer announces &quot; it is alright that we do not have a cleric, I'm a healer&quot;<br>
<br>
Your shadow knight wonders why the cleric is healing when He has dark empathy readied.<br>
<br>
Your bard keeps asking the ranger to call the spirit of the wolf for Him, then looks blankly at the cleric when He is asked to play a song to help soothe the spirit. ( mana regen song)<br>
<br>
Your bard says &quot; sit back and watch while i sing  ( kite ) the entire zone to death,&quot; and You are in Vox's lair facing the great dragon herself.<br>
<br>
Your warrior is about to die and the cleric says &quot; I can't heal, I'm smiting!&quot;<br>
<br>
Your wizard has just announced that He is a weapons master when it comes to the dagger ( 200 piercing), then leaps into battle with a yell of &quot; watch me fight!&quot;<br>
<br>
when Your warrior or rogue keeps saying they are out of spiritual energy ( mana ) and demands that they need Kodiac's Endless Intellect.<br>
<br>
when Your ONLY healer is a druid who believes He is a better warrior then the parties beastlord AND their pet COMBINED.<br>
<br>
when Your warrior is in His 30th season and has only now realized that His stanima has an affect on His health. ( hp )<br>
<br>
Your group has just asked the shadow knight to use dooming darkness to stop the creatures from running and She asks what that is.<br>
<br>
when Your monk announces He is the strongest there and He will carry all the treasure found on the hunt then sell and split with the group before You part ways. ( Main Loot)<br>
<br>
when the group leader turns to the Paladin and tells them to Lay Hands on the enemy when they get close to death and then turns to the Shadow Knight and orders them to Harm Touch the group's cleric if they get badly hurt.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
